import{z}from"zod";import{v4 as uuidv4}from"uuid";import{promises as fs}from"fs";import path from"path";import{checkWebSocketServerForUIProTool,getWebSocketServerForUIProTool}from"./utils.js";export const TOOL_SCHEMA_EXPORT_FIGMA_NODE=z.object({nodeId:z.string().optional(),format:z.enum(["SVG","PNG","JPG"]).optional(),scale:z.number().optional(),isBG:z.boolean().optional(),svgAsText:z.boolean().optional(),saveToPath:z.string().optional()});export const TOOL_NAME_EXPORT_FIGMA_NODE="exportFigmaNode";export const TOOL_DEFINITION_EXPORT_FIGMA_NODE={name:"exportFigmaNode",description:"Export a Figma node as an image in SVG, PNG, JPG format. Returns base64-encoded image data with MIME type. If no nodeId is provided, exports the first selected node in Figma.",inputSchema:{type:"object",properties:{nodeId:{type:"string",description:"Optional Figma node ID to export. If not provided, uses the first selected node."},format:{type:"string",enum:["SVG","PNG","JPG"],description:"Image format to export. Defaults to PNG."},scale:{type:"number",description:"Scale factor for export (e.g., 1, 2, 3). Defaults to 1."},isBG:{type:"boolean",description:"If true then image export will be without it's children (only export the background of the node). Default to false"},svgAsText:{type:"boolean",description:"If true and format is SVG, the SVG code will be returned as plain text instead of base64 image. Default to false."},saveToPath:{type:"string",description:"Optional file path to save the exported image quietly. When specified, the image will be saved to disk automatically and a confirmation message returned. Path can be relative or absolute."}},required:[]}};export async function runToolExportFigmaNode(args){try{const webSocketServer=getWebSocketServerForUIProTool(),serverCheckResult=checkWebSocketServerForUIProTool(webSocketServer);if(!serverCheckResult.valid)return serverCheckResult.data;const connectionManager=webSocketServer.getConnectionManager(),request={id:uuidv4(),type:"EXPORT_FIGMA_NODE",payload:{nodeId:args.nodeId,format:args.format||"PNG",scale:args.scale||1,isBG:args.isBG||!1,svgAsText:args.svgAsText||!1,saveToPath:args.saveToPath}},response=await connectionManager.sendRequest(request,6e4);if(!response.success||response.error)return{isError:!0,content:[{type:"text",text:`Error exporting node: ${response.error||"Unknown error"}`}]};if(!response.data)return{isError:!0,content:[{type:"text",text:"No image data received from Figma plugin. Make sure you have a node selected in Figma."}]};const{base64:base64,mimeType:mimeType,svgText:svgText}=response.data;if(args.saveToPath)try{const resolvedPath=path.isAbsolute(args.saveToPath)?args.saveToPath:path.join(process.cwd(),args.saveToPath),dir=path.dirname(resolvedPath);let dataToSave;return await fs.mkdir(dir,{recursive:!0}),dataToSave=svgText?Buffer.from(svgText,"utf-8"):Buffer.from(base64,"base64"),await fs.writeFile(resolvedPath,dataToSave),{content:[{type:"text",text:`Image saved to ${resolvedPath}`}]}}catch(saveError){return{isError:!0,content:[{type:"text",text:`Error saving image to ${args.saveToPath}: ${saveError.message||saveError}`}]}}return svgText?{content:[{type:"text",text:svgText}]}:{content:[{type:"image",data:base64,mimeType:mimeType}]}}catch(error){return{isError:!0,content:[{type:"text",text:`Error exporting node: ${error.message||error}`}]}}}